    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused BMW E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains composed thanks to a reinforced rear subframe and a recently refreshed suspension geometry. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. While showing minor patina consistent with its mileage, the mechanical vitals are robust, with consistent compression across all cylinders and a precise steering rack. A true enthusiast's example that balances raw performance with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
