      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride of ownership, offering a refined driving experience that belies its mileage. The exterior retains a beautiful, deep shine, though close inspection reveals minor road-wear consistent with careful use, such as small stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the upholstery is free of stains or tears, and every feature\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the heated seats\u2014operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service log. It has recently undergone a full multi-point inspection, including a fresh oil change and a brake system check, ensuring it is road-ready. It handles with precision and provides a quiet, comfortable ride, making it an ideal choice for someone seeking reliability without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
